<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<div><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Dear Manager,<br />
<br />
We are pleased to inform you that a new project has been officially approved by <strong>{{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Supervisor_User__r.Name}}}&nbsp;</strong>for the following lead.<br />
<br />
<strong>Lead Information:</strong></span></span></div>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Lead Name:&nbsp;<strong>{{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Lead__r.FirstName}}} {{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Lead__r.LastName}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Comapny<strong>: {{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Lead__r.Company}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Email: <strong>{{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Lead__r.Email}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Phone: <strong>{{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Lead__r.Phone}}}</strong></span></span></li>
</ul>

<div><br />
<span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>Site Visit Report Information:</strong></span></span></div>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Site Visit Report Number:&nbsp;<strong>{{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Name}}}&nbsp;</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Site Visit Supervisor:&nbsp;<strong>{{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Supervisor_User__r.Name}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Site Visit Date:&nbsp;<strong>{{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Site_Visit_Date__c}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Site Visit Time Slot:&nbsp;<strong>{{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Site_Visit_Time_Slot__c}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Supervisor Final&nbsp;Estimated&nbsp;Cost: <strong>{{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Total_Estimated_Cost__c}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Estimated Completion Months:&nbsp;<strong>{{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Estimated_Completion_Months__c}}}</strong></span></span></li>
</ul>

<div><br />
<span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Please review and update the site visit report. <a href="{{{siteVisitRecordPageLink}}}">Click</a> on the link to view the report.</span></span></div>

<div><br />
<br />
<span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Best Regards, &nbsp;<br />
<b>Arelia Living</b></span></span></div>
</body>
